2. FILE FORMAT INTEROPERABILITY AND CLEAN-ROOM STATEMENT
================================================================================

This software reads data files written by CPAP devices in order to display that
data to the person who owns the device and generated the data.

The parsers in this project were written independently from published standards,
publicly available format documentation, community reverse-engineering notes, and
inspection of data files produced by physically owned devices.

